<i>noun</i>: 해명 [해ː명], 천명 [천ː명] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>해명 [해ː명]</dt><br>
<dd>explanation; clarification; elucidation</dd><br>
<dd>이유나 내용 등을 풀어서 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of explaining or expounding reasons or details to someone.</dd><br>
<dt>천명 [천ː명]</dt><br>
<dd>clarification; elucidation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 사실이나 생각, 입장 등을 분명히 드러내어 밝힘.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of clarifying a fact, opinion, position, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>